{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "12", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "08", "M": "21", "S": "48"}}, "news": [{"title": "Brookfield India REIT's net operating income rises 23.8% in FY26", "para": "Brookfield India REIT reported a significant 53% year-on-year growth in net operating income to \u20b9742.9 crore for Q4 FY26. The company declared a distribution of \u20b95.50 per unit for the quarter, contributing to a full-year distribution of \u20b921.40 per unit. Strong leasing and the acquisition of Ecoworld bolstered performance, with net consolidated profit rising 30.81% for FY26.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/brookfield-india-reits-net-operating-income-rises-23-8-in-fy26/131028097?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-548999/131028097.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Maharashtra to digitise registration records from 1865; nearly 30 crore pages to go online", "para": "Maharashtra's Registration and Stamps Department is digitizing over a century of land records, aiming to convert 30 crore pages from 1865 onwards into a searchable digital format. This ambitious project will enhance property transparency, streamline transactions, and ensure long-term preservation of historical documents, making them accessible online for citizens.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/maharashtras-historic-land-records-to-go-digital-30-crore-pages-from-1865-to-transform-property-transactions/131027939?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-111522/131027939.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}, {"title": "Over 1,000 homes flout stilt parking norms in Gurugram, DLF phases top list", "para": "Gurugram authorities have launched a major crackdown on illegal use of stilt parking areas in